ScienceSeeker,collects,articles,from,science,blogs,around,the,world,allows,users,to,find,the,latest,science,news,and,discussion,on,any,topic,The,database,includes,more,than,blogs,and,posts,The,Search,API,lets,users,query,the,database,using,a,number,of,sorting,options,such,as,title,summary,number,of,recommendations,or,posts,talking,about,a,specific,peer,reviewed,article,Developers,can,integrate,the,functionality,of,the,API,with,third,party,sites,or,applications,It,uses,HTTP,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML